postcontent:
I am the owner of Gormark LLC, an FFL holder. I have multiple ads now up on this site warning people of the scams being committed by a group of people, some of whom claim to be me (or my business). They also claim that I am the FFL that will handle the transfer of the gun that they are selling. IT'S A SCAM!!! After a man from Colorado got ahold of me today I searched for the gun he was negotiating for and found 5 other ads by the same lister. Here are their ads today: Colt Combat Elite 45, Colt MkIV Series 80 Combat Elite 38 Super, Colt 1911 Talo XSE, Freedom Arms 83 Premier, Colt 1911 Series 80 Officers 3.5". Search for any one of these and click to see other listings by user. These are all scams! 

Copy some of the advertisement text and paste into a Google search window and you will likely find the original auction for this gun on another site. They take past auctions from other sites and just copy and paste, and put a good price on it.

Search for Gormark or Paula Cruz here on Armslist and you will see my other ads concerning this.
